Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.73,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It seems that I've been deemed valuable as a sex slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.69,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Being offered by a huge sum of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:37.69,Alternate,,0,0,0,,it looks like I've been resold by a slave trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:42.61,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I got sold to one slave market after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:48.12,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's an underground market\Nthat only keeps female sex slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.31,Alternate,,0,0,0,,A bunch of girls are taken in as slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.22,Alternate,,0,0,0,,They are treated as playthings and then cast aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.50,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a place where slave traders negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.92,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I thought that this was my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:06.89,Alternate,,0,0,0,,As a place where sex is involved,\Nnothing else tops this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.48,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This is a place where one can indulge in lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.51,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll find one of my own kind here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:18.58,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer staying longer here\Nrather than being sold off to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.60,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.72,Alternate,,0,0,0,,To get on the good side of the traders,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.14,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I should serve them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.68,Alternate,,0,0,0,,And then, I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.54,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I could already tell it at first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.69,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This girl has a lilith blood in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.80,Alternate,,0,0,0,,The blood she inherited hasn't been awakened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.43,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that she isn't aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:57.02,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can feel this nostalgia on my skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.64,Alternate,,0,0,0,,At last... I met one at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.78,Alternate,,0,0,0,,A fellow of my own kind.
